Problem Description: Spacewalk-install Tomcat service timeout error
  - Issue:
      Error Message: Tomcat failed to start properly or the installer ran out
      of tried. Please check /var/log/tomcat*/catlina.out for errors

  - Solution: Download c3p0-0.9.1.2-2.jpp5.noarch.rpm manually. Downgrade installed
    c3p0 version using "yum downgrade c3p0-0.9.1.2-2.jpp5.noarch.rpm".

  - Reference:
    [RHEL Bugzilla Bug 1442140](https://bugzilla.redhat.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1442140

  - Links:
    http://koji.spacewalkproject.org/kojifiles/packages/c3p0/0.9.1.2/2.jpp5/noarch/c3p0-0.9.1.2-2.jpp5.noarch.rpm
